---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Community"
  eyebrow="Tribe vibes"
  heading="The Duncit Community"
  intro="A growing crew of vibe-seekers, builders, hosts, and friends-of-friends."
  heroImage="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1543807535-eceef0bc6599?w=1600&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop"
>
  <h2>What's the vibe?</h2>
  <p>
    The Duncit community is welcoming, curious, and a little bit weird (in the best way).
    We celebrate the awkward small talk that becomes real friendship, the random meetups that
    turn into traditions, and the late-night DMs that change someone's week.
  </p>

  <h2>Ways to plug in</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Discord.</strong> Hang out, share memes, and meet the team in real time.</li>
    <li><strong>Beta program.</strong> Get early access and shape the app.</li>
    <li><strong>Local hosts.</strong> Run small meetups in your city — we'll help.</li>
    <li><strong>Creator collective.</strong> If you make stuff and want to collaborate, hi.</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="not-prose grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 my-6">
    <a href="#" class="block p-6 rounded-2xl bg-secondary text-white sticker hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition">
      <i class="fa-brands fa-discord text-3xl mb-2"></i>
      <div class="font-head font-bold text-xl">Join Discord</div>
      <div class="text-sm opacity-90 mt-1">12k+ members and counting</div>
    </a>
    <a href="/" class="block p-6 rounded-2xl bg-primary text-white sticker hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition">
      <i class="fa-solid fa-rocket text-3xl mb-2"></i>
      <div class="font-head font-bold text-xl">Beta waitlist</div>
      <div class="text-sm opacity-90 mt-1">Get in before everyone else</div>
    </a>
  </div>

  <h2>Read the rules</h2>
  <p>
    Before posting, please skim the <a href="/guidelines">community guidelines</a>.
    They're short and mostly common sense, but they keep the vibe right.
  </p>
</PageLayout>
